                            <comment id="12965229" author="team.fiveoh" created="Tue, 30 Nov 2010 14:24:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Same issue exists in 5.4.1. We are silently loosing messages if a queue is deleted via the console and the application continues to run. This behavior is not exactly ideal and I&apos;m surprised this issue has been open for a year.&lt;/p&gt;

